---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
const categories = [
  { name: '基礎知識',   slug: '基礎知識' },
  { name: '疾患別ケア', slug: '疾患別ケア' },
  { name: '家族向け',   slug: '家族向け' },
  { name: '制度・保険', slug: '制度・保険' },
  { name: 'キャリア',   slug: 'キャリア' },
  { name: '医療技術',   slug: '医療技術' },
];
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 mt-16">
  <!-- Top Section -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pt-12 pb-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">HOKAN STATION</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 max-w-sm">
          訪問看護に関わるすべての人へ。看護師・ケアマネジャー・ご家族・患者さんに役立つ専門情報を毎日発信しています。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Categories -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-semibold mb-4">カテゴリ</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {categories.map((cat) => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/category/${cat.slug}/`} class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary-500 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                {cat.name}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-semibold mb-4">サイト情報</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/about/" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">このサイトについて</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy/" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sitemap-index.xml" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">サイトマップ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom Bar -->
  <div class="border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-gray-600">
      <p>© {currentYear} HOKAN STATION. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>本サイトの情報は医療アドバイスに代わるものではありません。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
